## Priority Order

1. **Fix #4 (Delays)** — 5 min change, immediate ban risk reduction ✅
2. **Fix #1 (Browser Fingerprint)** — 2 line change, significant trust boost ✅
3. **Fix #3 (Reconnect Backoff)** — ~30 min, prevents account gets hammered ✅
4. **Fix #2 (Redis Auth State)** — ~2-3 hours, resolves Gaps #2 & #5 as one piece ✅
5. **Fix #6 (Redis Daily Counter)** — 15 min, perf win ✅
6. **Fix #7 (Session Heartbeat)** — Only needed if you plan to run cluster mode ✅
7. **Fix #8 (Residential Proxy Layer)** — 3-4 hours, the biggest trust boost ✅

